"25:1:8" : {s: 25, a: 1, w: 8, r: "علم", t: "لِلْعَٰلَمِينَ", l: "عَٰلَمِين", lc: 73, tl: "lilAAalameena", lb: "সকল জাতি, সৃষ্টিজগত",e: "to the worlds", b: "বিশ্ববাসীর জন্য", i: "", f: 3, rm: "to mark/sign/distinguish, creations/beings, world, science/learning/knowledge/information, aware/know. By means of which one knows a thing, hence it signifies world or creation, because by it the Creator is known. alim (pl. ulama) - one who is learned/wise or knows."},
